<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Locked - SecureBank</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .locked-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        }
        .locked-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .locked-icon {
            font-size: 5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .locked-title {
            color: #ef4444;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .locked-message {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="locked-container">
        <div class="locked-card">
            <div class="locked-icon">🔒</div>
            <h2 class="locked-title">Account Locked</h2>
            <p class="locked-message">
                Your account has been temporarily locked for security reasons. 
                This may be due to multiple failed login attempts or suspicious activity.
            </p>
            <p class="locked-message">
                Please contact our support team to unlock your account:
            </p>
            <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
                <p><strong>📞 Phone:</strong> +91-1800-XXX-XXXX</p>
                <p><strong>✉️ Email:</strong> support@securebank.com</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/auth/logout" class="btn-primary">Logout</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
